The original family is back operating Wings again! Woot woot! The food is always spot on, the family is great and friendly. Honestly some of the best Chinese food in the city.
Great food to say the least.  Everything was super fresh and huge servings! We ordered dinner for three which was so affordable and have tons of leftovers! We will definity be returning customers.
Under new management! Great Chinese food.  I was disappointed when Wing's was sold and renamed Wang's. Good news is it's back to Wing's!  Ginger beef and won ton soup is good.
